Configure health endpoints on Linux
Ignore this element.

1. 	
Start a terminal.
2. 	
As superuser, navigate to the Edge System installation directory: /opt/EdgeSystem.
3. 	
Type in the properties and their values through a command as shown in this example:

./OSIsoft.Data.System.Host Configuration System HealthEndpoints Endpoint=https://example.com/piwebapi/omf username=Test password=Test

4. 	
Optional: To view configured health endpoints, run this command:

./OSIsoft.Data.System.Host Configuration System HealthEndpoints

5. 	
Optional: To remove a configured health endpoint
a. 	
Copy the Id of the health endpoint that you want to remove.
b. 	
Run this command:

./OSIsoft.Data.System.Host Configuration System HealthEndpoints delete Id=Id




